snippet.title: Chase H.Q. 3D (PREVIEW)
snippet.description:
http://www.projectnext.de/
Title: Chase H.Q. 3D
By: Taito

Game INFO
Chase H.Q. 3D is the new 3D version of the original arcade game. With the help of Nancy, your operator, play an undercover cop to chase down and capture criminals.

For additional information visit: http://www.projectnext.de/thread.php?threadid=13367
